-- European Investment Bank to Provide Loan for China Climate Change Projects
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-12-03T06:12:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-03/european-investment-bank-to-provide-loan-for-china-climate-change-projects.html
The European Investment Bank has
agreed to provide a loan for climate change mitigation projects
in China, according to a press release distributed before a
briefing in Beijing today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
